<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-3">
        <%= image_tag "profile03.png", width: '100%', alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            <div class="progress">
              <div
              class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
              role="progressbar"
              aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
              aria-valuemax="100"
              style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
              >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-9">
        <p>Life-long learner seeking to co-create on interdisciplinary projects weaving innovation with practice, research and user engagement, providing clients with integrated solutions and value-added services.</p>

        <p>Aaron holds a MArch and BFA from the University of Houston, where he participated in the Graduate Design/Build Studio and a semester abroad at the University of Applied Arts, Vienna. He is a technical designer at a Houston based architecture firm.  His interests include art, design, and the virtual+built environments, with an emphasis on process, programming, aethetics, and development.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              JOB_I
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              JOB_II
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              JOB_III
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              JOB_IV
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              EDUCATION_I
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              EDUCATION_II
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              EDUCATION_III
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              EDUCATION_IV
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
